.TH TP-LINT 1 "February 2026" "tp-lint 1.5.2" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
tp-lint \- Translation Project linter and statistics tool
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tp-lint
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fILANG\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tp-lint
checks translation status against the GNU Translation Project matrix.
Shows coverage statistics and generates reports for translation teams.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version number and exit.
.TP
.BR \-l ", " \-\-list
List all available languages in the Translation Project matrix.
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-stats
Show comprehensive translation statistics for the specified language
or global statistics if no language is provided.
.TP
.BR \-d " " \fIDOMAIN\fR ", " \-\-domain " " \fIDOMAIN\fR
Filter results to show statistics for a specific package/domain only.
.TP
.BR \-n " " \fIN\fR ", " \-\-top " " \fIN\fR
Number of items to show in top/bottom ranking lists (default: 10).
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-report
Generate a comprehensive translation status report.
.TP
.BR \-\-report\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Report output format: markdown (default), html, text.
.TP
.BR \-\-report\-output " " \fIFILE\fR
Save generated report to the specified file instead of stdout.
.TP
.BR \-j ", " \-\-json
Output all results in JSON format for programmatic consumption.
.TP
.BR \-q ", " \-\-quiet
Suppress non-essential output, showing only key results and errors.
.TP
.BR \-f " " \fIFORMAT\fR ", " \-\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format: text (default), json, csv, tsv.
.TP
.BR \-\-strict
Treat warnings as errors and exit with non-zero status code.
.TP
.BR \-k ", " \-\-keep
Keep temporary files and cached data after processing.
.TP
.BR \-o " " \fIFILE\fR ", " \-\-output " " \fIFILE\fR
Save all output to the specified file instead of stdout.
.TP
.BR \-p " " \fIPACKAGE\fR ", " \-\-package " " \fIPACKAGE\fR
Focus analysis on a specific package or set of packages.
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-lint
Skip linting checks and show only statistical information.
.TP
.BR \-t ", " \-\-by\-translator
Group and sort results by translator instead of by package.
.TP
.BR \-V ", " \-\-verbose
Show detailed progress information, timing, and debug output.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
Error occurred.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Show global translation statistics:
.B tp-lint \-\-stats
.TP
Show statistics for Swedish:
.B tp-lint \-\-stats sv
.TP
Generate HTML report for German:
.B tp-lint \-\-report de \-\-report\-format html \-\-report\-output de.html
.TP
Check specific package:
.B tp-lint \-\-domain coreutils
